# =============================================================================
# 04-championship.http — Testes de Campeonatos
# =============================================================================
# Pré-requisito: adminToken + userId no env.json
# =============================================================================

### [1] Listar campeonatos (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/championship

###

### [2] Criar campeonato (Admin)
# @name createChamp
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/championship
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Campeonato Teste - Magic",
  "game": "Magic: The Gathering",
  "startDate": "2025-08-15T14:00:00Z",
  "entryFeeInCents": 2000,
  "maxParticipants": 16
}

### Após "Send Request", copie o id para championshipId no env.json

###

### [3] Buscar campeonato por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/championship/{{championshipId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### [4] Registrar participante no campeonato (Admin registra usuário)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/championship/{{championshipId}}/register
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "deckName": "Deck Azul Controle"
}

### Verifique: participante aparece na lista com playerNumber sequencial

###

### [5] Registrar o mesmo participante novamente — deve retornar 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/championship/{{championshipId}}/register
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "deckName": "Outro Deck"
}

###

### [6] Alterar status do campeonato para "EmAndamento"
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/championship/{{championshipId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "EmAndamento"
}

###

### [7] Alterar status para "Encerrado"
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/championship/{{championshipId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Encerrado"
}

###

### [8] Criar campeonato sem autenticação — deve retornar 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/championship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Campeonato Sem Auth",
  "game": "Pokemon",
  "startDate": "2025-09-01T10:00:00Z",
  "entryFeeInCents": 1000
}

###

### [9] Criar campeonato sem ser Admin — deve retornar 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/championship
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Campeonato Sem Permissão",
  "game": "Pokemon",
  "startDate": "2025-09-01T10:00:00Z",
  "entryFeeInCents": 1000
}

###
